commit.title: [schemes] Update indtables directly from declare.
commit.message:
[schemes] Update indtables directly from declare.

This was suggested by Pierre-Marie and indeed it does make sense,
tactics creating schemes are first consumers of `Declare` which is a
sub-consumer of the scheme registration machinery.
